    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1885-08-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1885-08-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="19" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d19">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">No. 19.</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Vienna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-08-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 4,
                            1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Lee reports that the minister for foreign affairs has declared that he
                        cannot receive Mr. Keiley, and has asked that the United States appoint
                        another minister.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
